(36, 'document', 'text/html', 'Rasul Mud Treatment', 'Rasul Mud Treatment', '', 'rasul-mud-treatment', '', 1, 0, 0, 4, 0, 'Rasul is a thermal treatment in which enriched muds are self-applied, usually in groups of 2-4 in a specialized room featuring steam vents and a rain roof. The treatment appears to be very popular in the UK and many of the top spas in England feature Rasul treatments. The treatment is fairly uncommon elsewhere. ', '<h4>TOP SPAS</h4>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="211">\r\n<p><a title="Monastero Santa Rosa Spa" href="http://monasterosantarosa.com/" target="_blank">Monastero Santa Rosa Spa</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="174">\r\n<p>Italy</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="211">\r\n<p><a title="Lakeside Spa" href="http://www.lakesideday.com/" target="_blank">Lakeside Spa</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="174">\r\n<p>UK</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="211">\r\n<p><a title="Fairlawns Spa" href="http://www.fairlawns.co.uk/" target="_blank">Fairlawns Spa</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="174">\r\n<p>UK</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="211">\r\n<p><a title="Champneys Henlow" href="http://www.champneys.com/Henlow" target="_blank">Champneys Henlow</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="174">\r\n<p>UK</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="211">\r\n<p><a title="Landmark Mandarin Oriental" href="http://www.mandarinoriental.com/landmark/" target="_blank">Landmark Mandarin Oriental</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="174">\r\n<p>Hong Kong</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="211">\r\n<p><a title="Cleopatra''s Spa" href="http://cleopatrasspaandwellness.com/eng_contact_us.aspx" target="_blank">Cleopatra''s Spa</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="174">\r\n<p>United Arab Emirates</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="211">\r\n<p><a title="Saxon Boutique Spa" href="http://www.saxon.co.za/" target="_blank">Saxon Boutique Spa</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="174">\r\n<p>South Africa</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="211">\r\n<p><a title="Twelve Apostles Spa" href="http://www.12apostleshotel.com/" target="_blank">Twelve Apostles Spa</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="174">\r\n<p>South Africa</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h4>TREATMENT OVERVIEW</h4>\r\n<p>The Rasul treatment lasts for about 45mins and begins with the participants entering the Rasul Treatment Chamber, a small thermal room, usually featuring Turkish tiles and a table in the center of the room for the muds.   </p>\r\n<p>Some Spas offer a salt-rub to exfoliate before the treatment to ensure that the skin absorbs all minerals, but this treatment is not essential to the experience.</p>\r\n<p>The treatment specialist leads the participants to the chamber and leaves them to self-apply the muds after walking them through the procedure.   </p>\r\n<p>Once the mud has been applied, the room is heated from 34 C (93.2 F) – 40 C (104 F) in order to dry the mud. The chamber is then filled with steam (increasing humidity from 50% - 100%) in order to soften the mud and allow the skin to absorb the minerals. The participants are kept in this state for about 25 mins. A gentle “rain” begins to fall from a specialized “rain roof” from which small droplets of water are emitted to wash the applied mud away. Some Spas use a rain shower, but all the top destinations feature this specialized system. Participants are then led to shower and attend another treatment of their choice.</p>\r\n<p>Guests can participate in this treatment up to 3 times a month.     </p>\r\n<h4>TECHNICAL SPECS</h4>\r\n<p>Once source* suggests that at minimum, the room should be 7m2 for 2 people.</p>\r\n<p>Heated seats (2-4 people)</p>\r\n<p>Steam vents</p>\r\n<p>Heated room</p>\r\n<p>Rain roof system</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h5>Muds</h5>\r\n<p>Up to six muds can be used, though most Spa’s supply between 3-5   </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Alpha Mud (Face)<br />Beta Mud (Upper Body, Neck, Bust)<br />Delta Mud (Feet &amp; Elbows)<br />Epsilon Mud (Back &amp; Legs)<br />Gamma Mud (Abdomen)<br />Zeta (Arms)</p>\r\n<h4>Sources &amp; Further Reading</h4>\r\n<p><a title="Spa Finder" href="http://www.spafinder.com/all-spas/N=0&amp;keywords=rasul" target="_blank">Spa Finder</a><br /><a title="Nola 7" href="http://nola7.com/en/wellness/view/124" target="_blank">Nola 7 Wellness and Spa Consultants</a><br /><a title="Aroma Leisure Spa Suppliers (muds)" href="http://aromaleisure.dns-systems.net/treatment-muds/" target="_blank">Aroma Leisure Spa Suppliers (muds)</a><br /><a title="Willow Stream Treatment Room Datasheet" href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=2&amp;ved=0CDoQFjAB&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fsystem.netsuite.com%2Fcore%2Fmedia%2Fmedia.nl%3Fid%3D83440%26c%3D581183%26h%3Db5741f98eaa00d51d4cd%26_xt%3D.pdf%26gc%3Dclear&amp;ei=5lBwUYLvErLB4AO4yYH4DQ&amp;usg=AFQjCNETUAI9uGJ6Zcf9bu4-33y5BegZmQ&amp;sig2=rIBuCtJ32UpDkU7-i4u7jA&amp;bvm=bv.45373924,d.dmg&amp;cad=rja">* Willow Stream Treatment Room Datasheet</a></p>', 1, 11, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1366316658, 30, 1372437776, 0, 0, 0, 1366316640, 1, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'web', 1, 'research-categories/wellness/rasul-mud-treatment.html', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(59, 'document', 'text/html', 'Noma in the Andes', 'Noma in the Andes', '', 'noma-in-the-andes', '', 1, 0, 0, 5, 0, '', '<p>Financed by <a title="NOma" href="http://noma.dk/">Noma</a> co-founder Claus Meyer, <a title="Restaurant Gustu" href="http://restaurantgustu.com/" target="_blank">Gustu</a> is part restaurant, part social venture. Applying the principals of strictly local and indigenous ingredients to the Amazon and Andes, Gustu goes one step further and exclusively employs cooks and waiters from Bolivia’s marginalized youth. He hopes this will demonstrate his conviction that the restaurant can be a powerful force for good while also offering local youth a priceless education in what has become the gold standard in international cuisine.</p>', 1, 10, 4, 1, 1, 1, 1370025553, 1, 1384878433, 0, 0, 0, 1370029140, 1, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'web', 1, 'research-categories/articles/noma-in-the-andes.html', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
